{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "马如龙发现张老实脚上带泥、行迹神秘，正想让杂货店休业，却被谢玉宝和铁震天劝阻：越是暴露身份，越要照常开门，才能让绝大师一方摸不清虚实。铁震天痛恨绝大师伪善，却被困局所限；谢玉宝则质问马如龙让她不明不白陪死是否问心无愧，并要求他归还自己的真面目和武功。第一个主顾是怀孕小媳妇，她突然要买三十斤盐，马如龙拒绝对孕妇动粗，张老实以盐已卖光打发她离开。铁震天判断这等于暴露自己藏身，很快第二个嘶哑低沉的大主顾上门，要买下店里所有东西。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "今天我们休业一天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "今天是不是过节？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "今天我们家里有喜事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那么今天我们为什么不开门？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "因为我是这里的老板。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我说今天不开门，就不开门。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "今天我们还是照常开门，他说的话不算数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我说的话为什么不算数？\n\n你为什么要管我的闲事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不是我要管，是你这位朋友要我管的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为今天你这杂货店一定要开门，非开门不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "现在他们已经知道我是马如龙，是这杂货店的老板，随时都可能来找我，我为什么还要开门放他们进来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "就因为他们知道你在这里，所以你非开门不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为杂货店若是不开门，他们就一定会闯进来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在我们将门户大张，他们反而摸不透我们的虚实，反而不敢轻举妄动了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "看来这地方每个人好像都比你想得周到得多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "在外面扫地的那个人，就是你的伙计。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "是个老实人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他的名字就叫张老实。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我喜欢老实人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只有老实人，才能骗得过那些奸诈多疑的阴险小人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他相信你就是马如龙，他还是可以先杀铁震天，再杀马如龙，如果他敢这么做，我反而佩服他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是他不敢，因为他不敢当着别人的面，做出食言背信的事，他要让天下人都确信他绝对是个嫉恶如仇的正直君子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我只恨不能将这样的君子刀刀斩尽，个个杀绝。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "只可惜这样的君子你连一个都杀不了，你自己反而快死了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "就算他们现在摸不透这里的虚实，还不敢轻举妄动，但一定已将杂货店包围，你们也休想冲得出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "所以你们只有在这里等，我也只有陪着你们在这里等，反正他们迟早会来的，说不定现在就已准备先派人来刺探这里的虚实。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "要刺探这里的虚实并不难，因为这里是个杂货店，任何人都可以来买东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "等他们来的时候，我好像也只有陪你们一起死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我不管你以前是不是真的做过那些事，我只想问你一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你让我这么样不明不白的陪你死，你自己心里能不能问心无愧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我可以告诉他们，你是无辜的，",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我可以先把你送走。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你能把我送到哪里去？他们会相信我是无辜的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你要我像野狗般被他们捉去，受他们拷打盘问？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你要我怎么做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我只要你还我几样东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "还你什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "还我真面目，还我的武功。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这些东西我也不知是被你用什么法子骗走的，如果你还有一点良心的话，现在你就应该全部还给我。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "看来你们的杂货店已经有主顾上门了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你去看看他是来买什么的？是真的来买杂货？\n\n还是想来买我们的命。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "她是个老主顾，每天都来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "每天都来的？来买什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "来买红糖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "她总认为红糖就像是人参一样，不但滋补，而且能治百病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我知道你一定会奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "因为我今天不买红糖。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_fu",
      "text": "你买什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "买盐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xi_fu",
      "text": "你要买多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "今天我们家要腌肉，腌得越咸，越不会走味。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我要买三十斤盐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你要她进来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她不肯进来，就抓她进来。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你为什么不去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "她是个大肚子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
